tinyrequest (1.0.0) stable; urgency=medium

  * Initial stable release of TinyRequest HTTP Client
  
  [ Core Features ]
  * Complete HTTP method support (GET, POST, PUT, DELETE, PATCH, HEAD, OPTIONS)
  * Advanced authentication system (API Key, Bearer Token, Basic Auth, OAuth 2.0)
  * Request collections for organizing API endpoints
  * Smart cookie management with automatic session handling
  * Real-time response display with comprehensive error handling
  
  [ User Interface ]
  * Modern GUI built with Dear ImGui v1.92.1 and GLFW3
  * Clean three-tab interface (Collections, Request, Response)
  * Font Awesome icons throughout the interface
  * Responsive design with collapsible panels
  * Custom theming with modern color scheme
  
  [ Data Management ]
  * Auto-save functionality with configurable intervals
  * JSON-based persistence with cJSON v1.7.15
  * Import/Export functionality for sharing collections
  * Legacy data migration support
  * Comprehensive backup and recovery system
  
  [ Network Features ]
  * SSL/TLS support with configurable certificate validation
  * libcurl-based HTTP client with advanced error handling
  * Response size limits and progress tracking
  * Connection timeout and retry mechanisms
  * Comprehensive URL validation
  
  [ Developer Features ]
  * Built with C11 and C++17 for optimal performance
  * Memory leak prevention and validation
  * Cross-distribution Linux support (Ubuntu, Fedora, Arch, openSUSE)
  * CMake-based build system with automated dependency management
  * Comprehensive documentation and contribution guidelines
  
  [ System Integration ]
  * Native Linux application with minimal dependencies
  * Proper desktop integration with .desktop files
  * Debian package with complete dependency management
  * Resource usage optimization (~50MB RAM, ~10MB disk)

 -- dexter-xD <https://github.com/dexter-xD>  Wed, 08 Jan 2025 12:00:00 +0530